173,open,Rename to reflect tracking and prioritizing tidying work,"DECISION: Rename to 'tendrils' with command 'tend' or 'td'.

Rationale: Tendrils captures both the gardening/tending metaphor (ongoing care, cultivation) and the spiral/cyclical nature of recursive self-improvement. The tool is a system for recursive self-improvement of a codebase, tracking pain (pain snake style), and prioritizing refactors.

